description: List existing versions of an Amazon SageMaker Model Card.

parameters.name: ModelCardName
parameters.description: List model card versions for the model card with the specified name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN).

nested_items.name: ModelCardVersionSummaryList
nested_items.description: The summaries of the listed versions of the model card.

nested_items.name: ModelCardName
nested_items.description: The name of the model card.

nested_items.name: ModelCardArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card.

nested_items.name: ModelCardStatus
nested_items.description: The approval status of the model card version within your organization. Different organizations might have different criteria for model card review and approval.
Draft: The model card is a work in progress.
PendingReview: The model card is pending review.
Approved: The model card is approved.
Archived: The model card is archived. No more updates should be made to the model card, but it can still be exported.

nested_items.name: ModelCardVersion
nested_items.description: A version of the model card.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the model card version was created.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: The time date and time that the model card version was last modified.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, SageMaker returns this token. To retrieve the next set of model card versions, use it in the subsequent request.
